{
  "stem": "3928.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I just show you this, you know, what sometimes personality can do to-- to-- to achieve things.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I-- giving me a-- a-- a-- what they call, a headquarters car, which was a Mercedes, with the two flags on the front, you know, with the German headquarters's flag and the regular German flag.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I used this car.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was my car to use whenever I go anywhere, whenever I, for every reason, I had to go.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At night, I went to Mr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Schweikert's place, on Rakoczi street.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "By this time, I had nothing to do with the man, my contact man, from Victory, because he disappeared off the scene.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Whatever happened to him, I never know, because my only contact was this Mr.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Schweikert.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and then, I took every day home papers from the German headquarters.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we typed it, in his office, as a safe conduct paper.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I had, with me, the great seal of the German headquarters, and I stamped it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the commander, Wiedemayer, signed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "His name, I signed on it, on every one of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now the paper was written in German purposely.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This is so the Hungarian Nazis could not question it, because it would have been Hungarian, they would have questioned it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But since it was German, 90% of them could not-- 99% of them couldn't read it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was written in German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it said these-- these people, whose name was on it, regardless that he's wearing the Jewish cross-- yeah, I mean the Magen David, is a important part of the German headquarters.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He works for the German headquarters and, as such, should not be, molested and shouldn't be harmed, signed Wiedemayer.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we made this paper out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was a safe conduct paper.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
